Columns.Name: QuestionResponseText
Columns.Description:
An Individual response to the associated question that cannot be addressed by a simple Question Response Rating and requires some amount of text that must be individually interpreted.

An example is a statement made in response to a Question as opposed to a standard "Yes/No" or scaled rating.

Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a service request/contact Communication.
